{"tid":914131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Bug王！微軟將推出Windows 10 Bug儀表板","createTime":"2018-11-24T04:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T11:37:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b021bfebe035ce865db6a4657811e4334f259fac","tid":914131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"IT之家11月24日消息 最近大家可能已經察覺到，Windows 10的Bug報告似乎越來越多了，這是因為Windows 10的Bug比之前多了嗎？而實際上是因為自從發生Windows 10更新十月版文件刪除bug後，微軟變得更加開放，會及時披露bug漏洞報告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/11/20181124_081852_663.jpg@wm_1,k_aW1nL3FkLnBuZw==,y_20,o_100,x_20,g_7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F11%2F20181124_081852_663.jpg%40wm_1%2Ck_aW1nL3FkLnBuZw%3D%3D%2Cy_20%2Co_100%2Cx_20%2Cg_7&h=6e270ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在，微軟已經承諾通過創建新的bug儀表板，使其成為Windows 10支持的永久功能，最終用戶和管理員可以使用該儀表板輕鬆查找系統當前的已知問題、解決方案以及微軟計劃修復它們的時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/396/661.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F396%2F661.htm&d=uJJZkqHGH4AVduFxQmeqIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=98a964b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/396/661.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dbd958c1d32d44831c9661da8c18a1fc04d7bf86","tid":914131,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:21:05.000Z","msg":"Apple 同 MS應該一齊go to die<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWorld no IT"},{"pid":"8fe8fe8c3bcd13285c232598b43c34d7a233dd11","tid":914131,"uid":67338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"MS正仆街<br />\n聯合硬件上,迫人用WIN10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\